00:17:31,270 --> 00:17:32,910
If you want to talk,

305
00:17:33,110 --> 00:17:35,310
I'm available anytime.

306
00:17:35,990 --> 00:17:36,720
Okay.

307
00:17:44,230 --> 00:17:45,300
Sleep early.

308
00:17:45,350 --> 00:17:45,910
Okay.

