00:19:33,330 --> 00:19:36,580
♫Blowing away my blues♫

334
00:19:36,930 --> 00:19:40,570
♫I see your clear features again♫

335
00:19:41,630 --> 00:19:47,070
♫Like stars illuminating the night sky♫

