00:19:47,470 --> 00:19:48,510
I'm full.

338
00:19:48,910 --> 00:19:50,230
Well, Shasha.

339
00:19:50,790 --> 00:19:51,590
What's wrong?

340
00:19:53,190 --> 00:19:54,590
Are you free later?

341
00:19:54,710 --> 00:19:56,550
Go have a cup of coffee with me.

342
00:19:59,110 --> 00:20:01,510
Mommy, I'm really fine.

343
00:20:01,590 --> 00:20:02,350
I can handle

344
00:20:02,350 --> 00:20:03,610
my own affairs myself.

345
00:20:04,110 --> 00:20:05,150
I know.

346
00:20:09,190 --> 00:20:11,190
It's just your aunt's family

347
00:20:11,230 --> 00:20:13,990
and Xiao Yicheng are coming to talk about their marriage.

348
00:20:13,990 --> 00:20:15,510
I don't want to be here.

349
00:20:19,630 --> 00:20:20,390
Okay.

350
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,230
I'll get changed.

351
00:21:07,350 --> 00:21:08,550
Why don't you go in?

352
00:21:13,720 --> 00:21:15,650
I haven't been back for a long time.

353
00:21:18,940 --> 00:21:19,670
Let's go.

354
00:21:20,030 --> 00:21:20,710
Let's go in.

355
00:21:37,510 --> 00:21:38,430
-You…
-Wenli.

356
00:21:42,590 --> 00:21:43,630
You go first.

357
00:21:50,230 --> 00:21:51,990
Are you feeling better?

358
00:21:52,630 --> 00:21:53,440
The doctor said

359
00:21:53,440 --> 00:21:55,770
I just need to pay attention to nutrition.

360
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:01,990
Dad.

361
00:22:04,430 --> 00:22:05,200
You're here.

362
00:22:05,310 --> 00:22:05,830
Dad.

363
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:08,990
Dad.

364
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:09,870
This

365
00:22:09,910 --> 00:22:11,310
is the finest Cordyceps.

366
00:22:11,350 --> 00:22:12,230
Wenli

367
00:22:12,270 --> 00:22:13,580
specially asked someone to buy it for you.

368
00:22:13,580 --> 00:22:15,830
Look, it must have cost you a lot.

369
00:22:16,030 --> 00:22:16,630
Not at all.

370
00:22:16,630 --> 00:22:17,870
It's all right.

371
00:22:17,950 --> 00:22:19,550
My mom was conferred the title of excellent teacher.

372
00:22:19,550 --> 00:22:20,470
There's a bonus.

373
00:22:20,470 --> 00:22:22,000
She bought it with that bonus.

374
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:23,270
You don't have to stand on ceremony

375
00:22:23,270 --> 00:22:24,470
coming back home.

376
00:22:24,750 --> 00:22:26,610
Don't buy things for me next time.

377
00:22:27,790 --> 00:22:29,150
Coming.

378
00:22:31,150 --> 00:22:32,350
Professor Gao asked me

379
00:22:32,350 --> 00:22:34,200
to buy candied dates early in the morning.

380
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:34,910
He said

381
00:22:34,910 --> 00:22:36,630
you've loved this since you were a kid, Wenli.

382
00:22:36,630 --> 00:22:37,990
Did you put rock candy in it?

383
00:22:37,990 --> 00:22:38,510
Yes.

384
00:22:38,580 --> 00:22:39,240
I made it

385
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:41,040
all according to Wenli's taste.

386
00:22:42,030 --> 00:22:43,110
Thank you, Dad.

387
00:22:44,150 --> 00:22:45,590
Wenli, have a sip.

388
00:22:56,390 --> 00:22:58,390
It's the taste of childhood, right?

389
00:23:06,710 --> 00:23:07,750
I'll try it too.

390
00:23:11,950 --> 00:23:12,550
Dad.

391
00:23:12,710 --> 00:23:13,590
Today,

392
00:23:13,630 --> 00:23:14,710
we're mainly here

393
00:23:14,870 --> 00:23:16,790
to talk about the kids' affair with the Xiao family.

394
00:23:16,790 --> 00:23:18,590
Before, Yicheng's parents

395
00:23:18,670 --> 00:23:19,510
said they were going

396
00:23:19,510 --> 00:23:21,150
to our hometown for marriage proposal.

397
00:23:21,150 --> 00:23:22,430
But Wenli thought

398
00:23:22,630 --> 00:23:23,540
it'd be a waste of their time

399
00:23:23,540 --> 00:23:24,750
to make that trip.

400
00:23:24,830 --> 00:23:25,710
Yes.

401
00:23:25,830 --> 00:23:26,920
Moreover,

402
00:23:26,990 --> 00:23:28,720
you are the elder of our family.

403
00:23:29,630 --> 00:23:31,390
I think

404
00:23:31,630 --> 00:23:33,310
it's the most appropriate

405
00:23:33,310 --> 00:23:35,270
and the best to talk about Xixi's marriage here at your place.

406
00:23:35,270 --> 00:23:36,310
It's good.

407
00:23:37,390 --> 00:23:38,590
The Xiao family

408
00:23:38,590 --> 00:23:40,230
are honest and kind.

409
00:23:40,390 --> 00:23:43,070
We should treat them well.

410
00:23:44,380 --> 00:23:45,350
And Xi,

411
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:46,590
you must control

412
00:23:46,590 --> 00:23:47,950
your bad temper.

413
00:23:49,550 --> 00:23:50,790
No matter how bad-tempered I am,

414
00:23:50,790 --> 00:23:52,120
I got it from you, right?

415
00:23:52,470 --> 00:23:53,190
Look.

416
00:23:53,270 --> 00:23:54,550
Look how petty she is.

417
00:23:54,790 --> 00:23:55,670
So vindictive.

418
00:23:55,790 --> 00:23:56,790
Professor Gao.

419
00:23:57,150 --> 00:23:58,880
Mr. Xiao and Mrs. Xiao are here.

420
00:23:59,270 --> 00:24:00,550
Come on. Come on.

421
00:24:00,550 --> 00:24:01,550
Have a seat.

422
00:24:01,830 --> 00:24:02,750
Go make coffee.

423
00:24:02,950 --> 00:24:03,810
Professor Gao.

424
00:24:03,870 --> 00:24:04,730
Professor Gao.

425
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:06,070
Uncle, Auntie.

426
00:24:06,150 --> 00:24:06,710
Auntie.

427
00:24:06,710 --> 00:24:07,630
Hello. Hello.

428
00:24:07,630 --> 00:24:08,230
You're here.

429
00:24:08,230 --> 00:24:09,830
-Come on. Have a seat.
-Okay.

430
00:24:15,270 --> 00:24:16,350
Professor Gao.

431
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:17,670
We are here

432
00:24:17,790 --> 00:24:19,440
with a mission today.

433
00:24:19,470 --> 00:24:20,790
Let's cut to the chase.

434
00:24:21,990 --> 00:24:23,470
It's a blessing for the Xiao family

435
00:24:23,470 --> 00:24:24,950
that Xixi is willing

436
00:24:25,030 --> 00:24:26,710
to marry Yicheng.

437
00:24:26,750 --> 00:24:27,510
So,

438
00:24:27,510 --> 00:24:29,390
we prepared a gift

439
00:24:30,430 --> 00:24:32,110
as a little something

440
00:24:32,190 --> 00:24:34,030
for our future daughter-in-law.

441
00:24:34,030 --> 00:24:34,590
Here.

442
00:24:38,140 --> 00:24:39,670
This is too much.

443
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,850
You gave us such an expensive gift.

444
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:49,590
You don't think

445
00:24:49,590 --> 00:24:51,390
I'm selling my daughter, do you?

446
00:24:51,830 --> 00:24:53,990
Mr. Lin, you must be joking.

447
00:24:54,190 --> 00:24:56,000
They are both the only child of our families.

448
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:57,680
Think of it as

449
00:24:57,710 --> 00:24:59,390
a gift

450
00:24:59,510 --> 00:25:00,990
prepared for our future grandson and granddaughter.

451
00:25:00,990 --> 00:25:03,070
Now our country has issued the three-child policy.

452
00:25:03,070 --> 00:25:06,150
The gift isn't enough to be divided among three children.

453
00:25:06,150 --> 00:25:07,110
This kid.

454
00:25:07,790 --> 00:25:09,150
With me as their grandfather,

455
00:25:09,150 --> 00:25:10,190
are you worried that

456
00:25:10,190 --> 00:25:12,390
the three of them won't be treated well?

457
00:25:12,590 --> 00:25:14,350
Lin, you haven't drunk yet.

458
00:25:14,390 --> 00:25:15,300
Yet you've started to talk nonsense.

459
00:25:15,300 --> 00:25:15,790
Look.

460
00:25:16,310 --> 00:25:17,150
You made my precious daughter

461
00:25:17,150 --> 00:25:17,950
blush.

462
00:25:18,590 --> 00:25:19,950
This is rare.

463
00:25:21,430 --> 00:25:22,430
No more jokes.

464
00:25:22,430 --> 00:25:23,070
If she doesn't want to get married,

465
00:25:23,070 --> 00:25:24,000
I'll be screwed.

466
00:25:40,870 --> 00:25:41,750
Mommy.

467
00:25:45,050 --> 00:25:47,180
If you have something to say, go ahead.

468
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:50,830
You have a personality,

469
00:25:51,070 --> 00:25:52,670
but you're not sharp-edged.

470
00:25:53,150 --> 00:25:54,150
But every time

471
00:25:54,150 --> 00:25:55,590
when it comes to Aunt,

472
00:25:55,670 --> 00:25:57,470
you become

473
00:25:58,790 --> 00:26:00,550
mean and bitter.

474
00:26:02,990 --> 00:26:04,230
Especially today.

475
00:26:04,230 --> 00:26:04,750
You knew

476
00:26:04,750 --> 00:26:06,430
Aunt and her family were coming,

477
00:26:06,430 --> 00:26:07,740
yet you took me out.

478
00:26:07,740 --> 00:26:09,870
It's not the right way to treat guests.

479
00:26:10,910 --> 00:26:12,430
Once their family comes,

480
00:26:14,310 --> 00:26:15,070
your grandpa

481
00:26:15,070 --> 00:26:16,630
can't see me anymore.

482
00:26:16,670 --> 00:26:19,470
I'll only be standing in their way if I stay at home.

483
00:26:19,670 --> 00:26:20,830
No, Mommy.

484
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:22,510
Why would you think so?

485
00:26:22,590 --> 00:26:24,510
Grandpa loves us.

486
00:26:25,670 --> 00:26:27,030
That's because you didn't see

487
00:26:27,030 --> 00:26:28,670
how good he is to your aunt.

488
00:26:29,390 --> 00:26:31,030
Your aunt has always been

489
00:26:31,030 --> 00:26:32,560
the pride of our Gao family.

490
00:26:32,590 --> 00:26:34,750
She's smart, pretty, talented,

491
00:26:34,750 --> 00:26:35,950
and graceful.

492
00:26:36,270 --> 00:26:37,630
But this daughter

493
00:26:37,710 --> 00:26:39,150
who he was so proud of

494
00:26:39,230 --> 00:26:40,790
ended up abandoning our family

495
00:26:40,790 --> 00:26:42,270
in order to marry a poor guy.

496
00:26:42,270 --> 00:26:44,470
That's why your grandpa was so angry.

497
00:26:45,110 --> 00:26:47,470
He's got tough love for her.

498
00:26:48,630 --> 00:26:50,350
But after 30 years,

499
00:26:50,550 --> 00:26:52,550
as soon as your aunt came back,

500
00:26:53,070 --> 00:26:55,000
your grandpa became biased again.

501
00:26:56,030 --> 00:26:57,560
I've been a filial daughter

502
00:26:57,710 --> 00:26:59,670
for 30 years for nothing.

503
00:27:00,190 --> 00:27:01,150
Mommy.

504
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:05,070
[Dad]

505
00:27:10,150 --> 00:27:10,950
Answer it.

506
00:27:17,230 --> 00:27:18,030
Dad.

507
00:27:18,470 --> 00:27:19,830
You've been hiding all day.

508
00:27:19,830 --> 00:27:21,090
It's time to come back.

509
00:27:22,430 --> 00:27:23,960
What are you talking about?

510
00:27:24,270 --> 00:27:24,870
Shasha and I

511
00:27:24,870 --> 00:27:26,930
are looking up information outside.

512
00:27:27,270 --> 00:27:28,350
Come back.

513
00:27:29,030 --> 00:27:30,830
We'll wait up for you for dinner.

514
00:27:35,030 --> 00:27:37,310
They've left?

515
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:41,990
Auntie Wang made soup for Shasha

516
00:27:42,470 --> 00:27:44,470
and your favorite ginger duck stew.

517
00:27:45,710 --> 00:27:46,430
Come back.

518
00:27:53,310 --> 00:27:54,510
See?

519
00:27:54,630 --> 00:27:56,710
Grandpa still cares about us.

520
00:27:57,670 --> 00:27:59,580
Let’s go home.

521
00:28:09,630 --> 00:28:10,830
Ling, come here.

522
00:28:10,830 --> 00:28:11,950
We've been waiting for you.

523
00:28:11,950 --> 00:28:13,110
Aunt. Uncle.

524
00:28:13,110 --> 00:28:13,750
Xixi.

525
00:28:15,390 --> 00:28:16,390
Where is Mr. Xiao?

526
00:28:17,020 --> 00:28:18,510
Something came up,

527
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:20,280
so Mr. Xiao and his family left.

528
00:28:20,630 --> 00:28:21,670
Don't call him

529
00:28:21,670 --> 00:28:22,950
Mr. Xiao anymore.

530
00:28:22,990 --> 00:28:24,270
We are family.

531
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:25,730
Call him brother-in-law.

532
00:28:27,990 --> 00:28:28,710
Dad.

533
00:28:29,070 --> 00:28:30,390
I was just about to

534
00:28:30,390 --> 00:28:31,390
call Shujun back.

535
00:28:31,390 --> 00:28:32,450
You guys eat first.

536
00:28:33,470 --> 00:28:33,950
Don't go.

537
00:28:33,950 --> 00:28:35,810
I said we've been waiting for you.

538
00:28:36,190 --> 00:28:36,950
-Yes.
-Sit down.

539
00:28:36,950 --> 00:28:37,480
Gao Ling.

540
00:28:37,550 --> 00:28:39,070
Look, Dad

541
00:28:39,110 --> 00:28:40,630
opened a bottle of fine wine today.

542
00:28:40,630 --> 00:28:41,750
We don't know much about wine.

543
00:28:41,750 --> 00:28:42,910
So, sit down

544
00:28:42,910 --> 00:28:44,040
and tell us about it.

545
00:28:44,190 --> 00:28:44,870
Sit down.

546
00:28:46,110 --> 00:28:47,110
Have a seat.

547
00:28:52,430 --> 00:28:54,440
I'm already 80 years old.

548
00:28:54,710 --> 00:28:56,430
I've waited for 30 years

549
00:28:56,590 --> 00:28:57,990
before the three of us

550
00:28:57,990 --> 00:28:59,910
could sit down and have dinner together.

551
00:28:59,910 --> 00:29:00,230
Yes.

552
00:29:00,230 --> 00:29:00,960
We don't know

553
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:02,510
when the next time will be.

554
00:29:02,750 --> 00:29:03,630
-Yes.
-Sit down.

555
00:29:03,630 --> 00:29:05,110
-Yes.
-Have a seat.

556
00:29:09,750 --> 00:29:10,710
Today

557
00:29:10,830 --> 00:29:11,910
is the day

558
00:29:11,910 --> 00:29:13,310
when the Gao family reunites.

559
00:29:13,310 --> 00:29:14,430
It's also when

560
00:29:14,550 --> 00:29:15,590
Xixi got engaged.

561
00:29:16,150 --> 00:29:16,790
This is

562
00:29:16,790 --> 00:29:18,790
a good day with double happy events.

563
00:29:18,910 --> 00:29:20,350
I'll drink up first.

564
00:29:25,590 --> 00:29:27,670
Since today is a good day,

565
00:29:27,910 --> 00:29:29,070
and since everyone is here,

566
00:29:29,070 --> 00:29:30,470
let's not let it pass

567
00:29:30,510 --> 00:29:32,110
without knowing any better.

568
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,710
Actually, I've always wanted to know

569
00:29:36,710 --> 00:29:38,710
why the book my mom translated

570
00:29:38,910 --> 00:29:40,440
doesn't have her name on it?

571
00:29:41,590 --> 00:29:42,550
Xixi.

572
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:44,510
It’s all in the past.

573
00:29:45,270 --> 00:29:46,600
It's in the past for you,

574
00:29:46,630 --> 00:29:47,750
but not for me.

575
00:29:47,750 --> 00:29:48,440
Xixi.

576
00:29:48,510 --> 00:29:49,510
It’s inappropriate to talk about this today.

577
00:29:49,510 --> 00:29:50,300
No, no.

578
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:52,890
This matter has to be explained

579
00:29:52,950 --> 00:29:55,030
sooner or later.

580
00:29:55,510 --> 00:29:56,350
Dad.

581
00:29:57,830 --> 00:29:58,790
Xixi.

582
00:29:59,350 --> 00:30:00,470
Here's the thing.

583
00:30:01,590 --> 00:30:03,590
Back then, when your mother

584
00:30:03,910 --> 00:30:05,550
wanted to marry your father,

585
00:30:06,190 --> 00:30:07,870
I was very against it.

586
00:30:08,670 --> 00:30:10,390
We had a huge fight.

587
00:30:10,390 --> 00:30:10,920
Dad...

588
00:30:10,990 --> 00:30:13,470
When this book was published,

589
00:30:14,020 --> 00:30:16,870
your mother wanted to run away from home.

